{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775828857531,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a3603c001FYhwhtt0TVyFUp","messageID":"msg_d77a348b8001NK557GTM8zgJ7y","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_7829e43658ae4fb5aefdcdb7","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project structure at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z. I need to understand:\n\n1. The overall project structure (directories, key files)\n2. What's in the pkg/router directory (if it exists)\n3. Any existing design.md files\n4. The tmp/agentcube-ref/ directory structure (if it exists)\n5. Any existing AR-010 or session management related files\n6. The go.mod file to understand dependencies\n7. Any existing architecture or design documents\n\nPlease provide a comprehensive overview of the project structure, focusing on the router package and session management related code. Return all findings in detail.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_2885c8e87ffe17uV1q4Fh875Ob (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nI now have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is the detailed report.\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Project Structure Overview: AgentCube\n\n### 1. Overall Project Structure\n\nThe project is located at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z` and is a Go module named `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`. It is a **Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents**.\n\n**Root-level directories:**\n\n| Directory | Purpose |\n|-----------|---------|\n| `pkg/` | Core Go packages (apis, common, router, store, workloadmanager) |\n| `client-go/` | Generated Kubernetes client (clientset, informers, listers) |\n| `changes/` | Change requests AR-001 through AR-010 (each with design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md, delta-spec.md) |\n| `session-routing/` | Session routing spec and design documents |\n| `session-store/` | Session store spec and design documents |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | Sandbox orchestration spec and design |\n| `code-execution/` | Code execution spec and design |\n| `deployment/` | Deployment spec and design |\n| `ci-cd/` | CI/CD spec and design |\n| `integrations/` | Integration spec and design |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | CLI toolkit spec and design |\n| `python-sdk/` | Python SDK spec and design |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | Idle cleanup spec and design |\n| `testing/` | TDD manifest |\n| `delta-spec.md` | Delta spec for AR-009 (Router HTTP reverse proxy core) |\n| `design.md` | Design document for AR-009 (Router) |\n| `proposal.md` | Proposal for AR-010 (Router session management) |\n| `project.md` | Project context document |\n\n**Root-level files:**\n- `go.mod` / `go.sum` -- Go module definition\n- `coverage.out` -- Test coverage output\n- `.sdd_prompt.md` -- SDD prompt file\n\n---\n\n### 2. The `pkg/router` Directory (12 files)\n\nLocated at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/router/`:\n\n| File | Lines | Purpose |\n|------|-------|---------|\n| `config.go` | 21 | `Config` struct (Port, Debug, EnableTLS, TLSCert, TLSKey, MaxConcurrentRequests) + `NewDefaultConfig()` |\n| `server.go` | 139 | `Server` struct, `NewServer()`, `Start()`, `Run()`, `Shutdown()`, route registration |\n| `session_manager.go` | 141 | `SessionManager` interface + `manager` implementation (GetSandboxBySession, createSandbox) |\n| `jwt.go` | 129 | `JWTManager` -- RSA 2048-bit key generation, RS256 JWT signing, K8s Secret storage |\n| `proxy.go` | 192 | Reverse proxy logic: `handleInvoke`, `handleAgentInvoke`, `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke`, `forwardToSandbox`, error handling |\n| `backend.go` | 92 | `Backend` struct + `BackendHealthChecker` (HTTP health checks with consecutive fail/success thresholds) |\n| `loadbalancer.go` | 100 | `LoadBalancer` interface, `RoundRobinBalancer`, `LeastConnectionsBalancer` |\n| `middleware.go` | 55 | `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware`, `RequestLoggerMiddleware`, `TraceIDMiddleware` |\n| `router.go` | 79 | `Router` interface + `routerImpl` (AddRoute, RemoveRoute, ServeHTTP with mutex-protected route map) |\n| `informer.go` | 84 | `InformerManager` -- SharedInformerFactory for AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRDs (event handlers are currently **stubs** -- only log at V(4)) |\n| `errors.go` | 33 | `SessionNotFoundError`, `SandboxTemplateNotFoundError` custom error types |\n| `health.go` | 18 | `handleHealthLive` (always 200), `handleHealthReady` (checks sessionManager availability) |\n\n**Key observations about pkg/router:**\n- The **informer.go event handlers are stubs** -- `onAgentRuntimeAdded`, `onAgentRuntimeUpdated`, etc. only log at V(4) and do not actually update the route table or store.\n- The **store.Storage() currently returns nil** (stub implementation).\n- The `Server` struct does NOT yet include `InformerManager` or `LifecycleManager` fields (those are planned for AR-010).\n- The `Config` struct does NOT yet include session lifecycle config fields (SessionCheckInterval, SessionIdleTimeout, SessionMaxDuration, StoreType).\n\n---\n\n### 3. Existing design.md Files\n\nThere are **21 design.md files** in total:\n\n**Root-level:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` -- **AR-009: Router HTTP reverse proxy core** (fully filled in, 411 lines)\n\n**Per-change-request (AR-001 through AR-010):**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-003/design.md`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/o