lcano-sh/agentcube`  \n**Go version:** 1.25.0\n\n**Direct dependencies:**\n| Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | v1.10.0 | HTTP web framework |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | v5.2.1 | RS256 JWT signing |\n| `github.com/google/uuid` | v1.6.0 | UUID generation (trace IDs) |\n| `github.com/prometheus/client_golang` | v1.22.0 | Metrics |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify` | v1.11.1 | Testing |\n| `golang.org/x/net` | v0.51.0 | HTTP/2 support |\n| `k8s.io/api` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes API types |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes apimachinery |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | v0.34.1 | Kubernetes client library |\n| `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` | v0.22.2 | Controller runtime |\n\nNotable: The go.mod does **not** yet include `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` or `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` -- these are planned for AR-010 but not yet added.\n\n---\n\n### 7. Architecture and Design Documents Summary\n\n**Primary architecture documents:**\n\n1. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md`** -- High-level project context. AgentCube is a K8s-native sandbox orchestration platform with Router, WorkloadManager, Redis/Valkey session store, Sandbox Pods, and Agentd idle cleanup controller.\n\n2. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md`** -- AR-009 detailed design (411 lines). Covers Config, Server, SessionManager, JWTManager, Router, Backend, LoadBalancer, HealthChecker, error types, API contracts, error handling, test strategy, implementation phases, and future changes (AR-010 through AR-014).\n\n3. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`** -- AR-010 proposal (234 lines). Covers session management purpose, in/out scope, impact analysis, risk assessment, 3 alternatives considered (with the Redis/Valkey + local cache approach selected), implementation notes with code sketches, and acceptance criteria.\n\n4. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md`** -- AR-009 delta spec (821 lines). Exhaustive Gherkin-style requirements for the router module.\n\n5. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md`** -- AR-010 delta spec (594 lines). Exhaustive requirements for session management expansion including SessionManager interface extension, Redis/Valkey Store implementation, Informer event handler activation, session lifecycle GC, proxy flow session awareness, Server integration, Config extension, and build/test gates.\n\n6. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-routing/design.md`** -- Session routing design (160 lines). Documents the current router package structure, Config, Server, SessionManager, JWT, proxy behavior, middleware, and environment variables.\n\n7. **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md`** -- Session store design (206 lines). Documents the Store interface, Redis and Valkey implementations, key naming conventions, environment variables, and operation summaries.\n\n---\n\n### 8. Key Supporting Packages\n\n**`pkg/store/store.go`** (23 lines):\n- Defines the `Store` interface with methods: `StoreSandbox`, `UpdateSandbox`, `DeleteSandboxBySessionID`, `GetSandbox`, `ListSandboxes`, `UpdateSessionLastActivity`\n- `ErrNotFound` sentinel error\n- `Storage()` currently returns `nil` (stub)\n\n**`pkg/common/types/types.go`** (14 lines):\n- Type aliases: `SandboxInfo` and `EntryPoint` point to `handler.SandboxInfo` and `handler.EntryPoint`\n- Constants: `AgentRuntimeKind`, `CodeInterpreterKind`, `SandboxKind`, `SandboxClaimKind`\n\n**`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go`** (71 lines):\n- Defines `CreateSandboxRequest`, `CreateSandboxResponse`, `EntryPoint`, `SandboxInfo`, `SandboxStatus`\n- `SandboxInfo` has fields: SessionID, SandboxName, SandboxID, WorkloadName, Namespace, Kind, PodIP, EntryPoints, CreatedAt, ExpiresAt, Status, LastActivityAt\n\n**`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`** (12 files):\n- CRD type definitions for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n- Group version info, constants, shared types, deep copy generation\n\n**`client-go/`** (3 subdirectories):\n- `clientset/` -- Generated typed Kubernetes client\n- `informers/` -- Shared informer factory\n- `listers/` -- Lister implementations\n\n---\n\n### 9. Change Request Progression (AR-001 through AR-010)\n\n| AR | Topic | Status |\n|----|-------|--------|\n| AR-001 | (base) | Design exists |\n| AR-002 | (base) | Design exists |\n| AR-003 | CRD type definitions | Design exists |\n| AR-004 | (base) | Design exists |\n| AR-005 | Sandbox creation | Design exists |\n| AR-006 | (base) | Design exists |\n| AR-007 | Reconciler controller | Design exists |\n| AR-008 | (base) | Design exists |\n| AR-009 | Router HTTP reverse proxy core | **Implemented** (code exists in pkg/router/) |\n| AR-010 | Router session management | **Spec complete, code not yet implemented** (stub informer handlers, stub store) |\n\n---\n\n### 10. Session Management -- Current State vs. AR-010 Requirements\n\n**What exists today (AR-009):**\n- `SessionManager` interface with single method `GetSandboxBySession`\n- `manager` implementation that looks up sessions from store or creates via WorkloadManager\n- `Store` interface defined but `Storage()` returns nil\n- Informer event handlers are stubs (only log)\n- Server has no `InformerManager` or `LifecycleManager` fields\n- Config has no session lifecycle fields\n\n**What AR-010 requires (from delta-spec.md):**\n1. **SessionManager interface expansion**: Add `CreateSession`, `UpdateSession`, `DeleteSession`, `UpdateLastActivity`, `ListSessions`\n2. **Redis/Valkey Store implementation**: Full backend with atomic pipelines, ZSET indices for expiry and last_activity\n3. **Informer event handler activation**: Actual route table updates, store updates, CR status mapping\n4. **Session lifecycle GC**: `LifecycleManager` with cleanupExpired, cleanupIdle, cleanupOrphans, cleanupGhosts\n5. **Proxy flow enhancement**: Two LastActivityAt updates per request, terminated session 410 responses, JWT injection for Sandbox/SandboxClaim kinds\n6. **Server integration**: Add InformerManager and LifecycleManager fields, start/stop lifecycle\n7. **Config extension**: SessionCheckInterval, SessionIdleTimeout, SessionMaxDuration, StoreType\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2885c8e87ffe17uV1q4Fh875Ob","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775828693365,"end":1775828857528}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775828857580,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a5f2ba001XmIsN14ikT0y3w","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d77a348b8001NK557GTM8zgJ7y","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":19663,"input":19251,"output":228,"reasoning":184,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.005993488}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775828858992,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a5f86d001lIEnxgLt85op10","messageID":"msg_d77a5f300001Om7ZmvJB7jSwFj","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775828862501,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a6019c001ywekT2tT4ASWda","messageID":"msg_d77a5f300001Om7ZmvJB7jSwFj","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_726e4a410d184fb9a7ed2922","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010: Router 会话管理 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，在 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的基础上，扩展 SessionManager 接口、实现 Redis/Valkey Store 后端、激活 Informer 事件处理器、引入会话生命周期 GC，并增强代理流程的会话感知能力。本变更是对 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的下游消费方，同时依赖 session-store spec 中定义的存储契约。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: SessionManager 接口扩展\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中扩展 `SessionManager` 接口，新增以下方法：\n12: \n13: ```go\n14: type SessionManager interface {\n15:     // 现有方法（AR-009）\n16:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n17: \n18:     // 新增方法（AR-010）\n19:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n20:     UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n21:     DeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n22:     UpdateLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n23:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n24: }\n25: ```\n26: \n27: `CreateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.StoreSandbox` 将会话元数据写入存储后端。\n28: \n29: `UpdateSession` SHALL 调用 `store.UpdateSandbox` 更新已存在会话的元数据。\n30: \n31: `DeleteSession` SHALL 调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 删除会话及关联索引。\n32: \n33: `UpdateLastActivity` SHALL 调用 `store.UpdateSessionLastActivity` 更新最后活跃时间。\n34: \n35: `ListSessions` SHALL 调用 `store.ListSandboxes` 返回所有活跃会话。\n36: \n37: #### Scenario: CreateSession 写入存储\n38: \n39: - **GIVEN** `SandboxInfo{SessionID: \"sess-001\", SandboxName: \"my-runtime-abc\", Kind: \"AgentRuntime\"}`\n40: - **WHEN** `CreateSession(ctx, info)` 被调用\n41: - **THEN** `store.StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", info)` 被调用且返回 nil\n42: \n43: #### Scenario: UpdateSession 更新已存在会话\n44: \n45: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n46: - **WHEN** `UpdateSession(ctx, \"sess-001\", updatedInfo)` 被调用\n47: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", updatedInfo)` 被调用\n48: \n49: #### Scenario: DeleteSession 清理会话\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n52: - **WHEN** `DeleteSession(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n53: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n54: \n55: #### Scenario: UpdateLastActivity 更新活跃时间\n56: \n57: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n58: - **WHEN** `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n59: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\", time.Now())` 被调用\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: ListSessions 返回所有会话\n62: \n63: - **GIVEN** 存储中存在 `sess-001` 和 `sess-002` 条目\n64: - **WHEN** `ListSessions(ctx)` 被调用\n65: - **THEN** 返回包含两个条目的 map，key 为 sessionID\n66: \n67: ---\n68: \n69: ### Requirement: Redis/Valkey Store 实现\n70: \n71: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/store/` 下实现 Redis 和 Valkey 两种后端，满足 session-store spec 中定义的契约：\n72: \n73: **接口契约：**\n74: \n75: | 方法 | 行为 |\n76: |------|------|\n77: | `StoreSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)` | SETNX session key + ZADD expiry + ZADD last_activity（原子管道） |\n78: | `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sessionID, info)` | SET XX（仅更新已存在的 key，不修改 ZSET） |\n79: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID)` | DEL session key + ZREM expiry + ZREM last_activity（原子管道） |\n80: | `GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` | GET session key，不存在返回 `ErrNotFound` |\n81: | `ListSandboxes(ctx)` | 遍历 `session:expiry` ZSET 加载所有会话 |\n82: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)` | 验证 session key 存在后 ZADD last_activity |\n83: \n84: **Key 命名规范：**\n85: - 主键：`session:{sessionID}`（JSON 文档）\n86: - 过期索引：`session:expiry`（sorted set，score = ExpiresAt Unix 秒）\n87: - 活跃索引：`session:last_activity`（sorted set，score = last activity Unix 秒）\n88: \n89: **Provider 选择：**\n90: - 环境变量 `STORE_TYPE`（大小写不敏感），未设置时默认 `redis`\n91: - 支持值：`redis`、`valkey`，其他值初始化失败\n92: \n93: **Redis 配置：**\n94: - 必需：`REDIS_ADDR`\n95: - 默认要求密码：`REDIS_PASSWORD` 非空，除非 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\n96: \n97: **Valkey 配置：**\n98: - 必需：`VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔，split 为 `InitAddress`）\n99: - 默认要求密码：`VALKEY_PASSWORD` 非空，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\n100: - 可选：`VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true` → `DisableCache`，`VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE=true` → `ForceSingleClient`\n101: \n102: **单例访问：**\n103: - `Storage()` 使用 `sync.Once` 初始化\n104: - 初始化失败时通过 `klog.Fatal` 记录\n105: \n106: #### Scenario: 默认 Provider 为 Redis\n107: \n108: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` 未设置\n109: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次调用\n110: - **THEN** 构造 Redis 实现\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: 主键命名\n113: \n114: - **GIVEN** sessionID 为 `abc`\n115: - **WHEN** Store 写入会话数据\n116: - **THEN** Redis key 为 `session:abc`\n117: \n118: #### Scenario: 过期索引 ZADD\n119: \n120: - **GIVEN** SandboxInfo 的 ExpiresAt 为 `2026-04-10T10:00:00Z`（Unix 秒 1744279200）\n121: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n122: - **THEN** `session:expiry` ZSET 中 member `abc` 的 score 为 `1744279200`\n123: \n124: #### Scenario: 活跃索引 ZADD\n125: \n126: - **GIVEN** 当前时间为 `2026-04-10T09:00:00Z`（Unix 秒 1744275600）\n127: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n128: - **THEN** `session:last_activity` ZSET 中 member `abc` 的 score 为 `1744275600`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: 获取不存在的会话返回 ErrNotFound\n131: \n132: - **GIVEN** `session:unknown` key 不存在\n133: - **WHEN** `GetSandbox(ctx, \"unknown\")` 被调用\n134: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: nil Sandbox 被拒绝\n137: \n138: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", nil)`\n139: - **WHEN** 被调用\n140: - **THEN** 返回错误，指示 sandbox 为 nil\n141: \n142: #### Scenario: UpdateSandbox 对不存在的 key 返回错误\n143: \n144: - **GIVEN** `session:unknown` key 不存在\n145: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox(ctx, \"unknown\", info)` 被调用\n146: - **THEN** 返回错误（Redis: SET XX 返回 false → `key not exists`）\n147: \n148: #### Scenario: 删除操作清理所有关联 key\n149: \n150: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 存在于主键和两个 ZSET 中\n151: - **WHEN** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 执行成功\n152: - **THEN** `GET session:sess-001` 返回 nil，两个 ZSET 中均不包含 `sess-001`\n153: \n154: #### Scenario: Valkey 多地址解析\n155: \n156: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR = \"valkey1:6379,valkey2:6379,valkey3:6379\"`\n157: - **WHEN** Valkey Store 初始化\n158: - **THEN** `InitAddress` 包含三个地址\n159: \n160: #### Scenario: 不支持的 STORE_TYPE 初始化失败\n161: \n162: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE = \"memcached\"`\n163: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次调用\n164: - **THEN** 初始化失败，记录 fatal 日志\n165: \n166: #### Scenario: 并发调用 Storage() 仅初始化一次\n167: \n168: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 同时调用 `Storage()`\n169: - **WHEN** 执行完成\n170: - **THEN** `initStore` 仅执行一次，所有调用返回同一实例\n171: \n172: ---\n173: \n174: ### Requirement: StoreSandbox 原子性\n175: \n176: The system SHALL 在 `StoreSandbox` 中使用 Redis pipeline 或 Valkey multi block 确保以下操作的原子性：\n177: 1. SETNX `session:{sessionID}` 写入 JSON 文档\n178: 2. ZADD `session:expiry` 添加过期索引\n179: 3. ZADD `session:last_activity` 添加活跃索引\n180: \n181: 若管道中任一命令失败，整个操作 SHALL 失败，不产生部分写入。\n182: \n183: #### Scenario: 原子写入成功\n184: \n185: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 连接正常\n186: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, \"sess-001\", validInfo)` 被调用\n187: - **THEN** 三个命令在一个管道中执行，全部成功\n188: \n189: #### Scenario: 原子写入部分失败回滚\n190: \n191: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 在管道执行过程中断开连接\n192: - **WHEN** `StoreSandbox` 执行\n193: - **THEN** 返回错误，不产生部分写入（SETNX 未执行则 ZSET 不写入）\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: ### Requirement: UpdateSessionLastActivity 前置检查\n198: \n199: The system SHALL 在 `UpdateSessionLastActivity` 中执行以下检查：\n200: 1. 若 `sessionID` 为空，返回错误\n201: 2. 若 `at` 为零时间（`time.IsZero()`），使用 `time.Now()`\n202: 3. 验证 `session:{sessionID}` key 存在，不存在返回 `ErrNotFound`\n203: 4. 执行 ZADD `session:last_activity` 更新活跃索引\n204: \n205: #### Scenario: 空 sessionID 被拒绝\n206: \n207: - **GIVEN** `sessionID = \"\"`\n208: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"\", time.Now())` 被调用\n209: - **THEN** 返回错误\n210: \n211: #### Scenario: 零时间自动使用当前时间\n212: \n213: - **GIVEN** `at = time.Time{}`（零时间）\n214: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-001\", at)` 被调用\n215: - **THEN** 使用 `time.Now()` 作为 score\n216: \n217: #### Scenario: 未知会话的活跃时间更新\n218: \n219: - **GIVEN** `session:sess-unknown` key 不存在\n220: - **WHEN** `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"sess-unknown\", time.Now())` 被调用\n221: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n222: \n223: ---\n224: \n225: ### Requirement: ListExpiredSandboxes 与 ListInactiveSandboxes\n226: \n227: The system SHALL 在 Store 接口中新增以下方法（供 GC 使用）：\n228: \n229: ```go\n230: ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n231: ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n232: ```\n233: \n234: `ListExpiredSandboxes` SHALL 使用 `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf <before.Unix()> LIMIT 0 <limit>` 查询过期会话 ID，然后批量加载 JSON 文档。\n235: \n236: `ListInactiveSandboxes` SHALL 使用 `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity -inf <before.Unix()> LIMIT 0 <limit>` 查询不活跃会话 ID，然后批量加载 JSON 文档。\n237: \n238: 加载 JSON 时若某个 session ID 对应的主键不存在（孤立 ZSET 成员），SHALL 跳过该条目而不使整个批次失败。\n239: \n240: #### Scenario: 查询过期会话\n241: \n242: - **GIVEN** `session:expiry` 中有 `sess-001`（score=1000）和 `sess-002`（score=2000）\n243: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Unix(1500, 0), 10)` 被调用\n244: - **THEN** 返回 `sess-001` 的 SandboxInfo，不包含 `sess-002`\n245: \n246: #### Scenario: 孤立 ZSET 成员被跳过\n247: \n248: - **GIVEN** `session:expiry` 中有 `sess-orphan`，但 `session:sess-orphan` key 不存在\n249: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes` 执行\n250: - **THEN** `sess-orphan` 被跳过，不返回错误\n251: \n252: ---\n253: \n254: ### Requirement: Informer 事件处理器激活\n255: \n256: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/informer.go` 中将 Informer 事件处理器从 stub 改为实际更新会话缓存和路由表：\n257: \n258: **AgentRuntime 事件处理：**\n259: \n260: | 事件 | 行为 |\n261: |------|------|\n262: | `AddFunc` | 从 CR labels 提取 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id`，构建 `SandboxInfo`，调用 `router.AddRoute` 注册路由 |\n263: | `UpdateFunc` | 比较新旧 CR 的 `status.conditions`，若 `Ready` 条件变更，调用 `store.UpdateSandbox` 更新会话状态 |\n264: | `DeleteFunc` | 从 CR labels 或 tombstone 提取 session-id，调用 `router.RemoveRoute` 和 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` |\n265: \n266: **CodeInterpreter 事件处理：**\n267: \n268: | 事件 | 行为 |\n269: |------|------|\n270: | `AddFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime AddFunc，Kind 标识为 `CodeInterpreter` |\n271: | `UpdateFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime UpdateFunc，额外处理 Warm Pool 激活事件（`spec.warmPoolSize` 从 0 变为 >0） |\n272: | `DeleteFunc` | 同 AgentRuntime DeleteFunc |\n273: \n274: **Label 提取：**\n275: - `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` → `SandboxInfo.SessionID`\n276: - `runtime.agentcube.io/sandbox-name` → `SandboxInfo.SandboxName`\n277: - `runtime.agentcube.io/workload-name` → `SandboxInfo.WorkloadName`\n278: \n279: **状态映射（CR conditions → Store status）：**\n280: \n281: | Ready Condition | Store Status |\n282: |-----------------|--------------|\n283: | 缺失             | `pending`    |\n284: | `status: Unknown` | `pending`    |\n285: | `status: True`   | `running`    |\n286: | `status: False`, `reason: Terminated` | `terminated` |\n287: | `status: False`, 其他 reason | `pending` |\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 新增时注册路由\n290: \n291: - **GIVEN** 新的 AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime`，labels 包含 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-001`\n292: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被触发\n293: - **THEN** 构建 `SandboxInfo{SessionID: \"sess-001\", Kind: \"AgentRuntime\", Status: \"pending\"}`\n294: - **AND** `router.AddRoute` 被调用注册对应路由\n295: \n296: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 状态从 Pending 变为 Running\n297: \n298: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 的 `status.conditions` 中 `Ready` 条件从缺失变为 `True`\n299: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeUpdated` 被触发\n300: - **THEN** `store.UpdateSandbox` 被调用，将会话状态更新为 `running`\n301: \n302: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 删除时清理路由和存储\n303: \n304: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime` 被删除，labels 包含 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id: sess-001`\n305: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeDeleted` 被触发\n306: - **THEN** `router.RemoveRoute` 被调用移除路由\n307: - **AND** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n308: \n309: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter Warm Pool 激活\n310: \n311: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter CR 的 `spec.warmPoolSize` 从 0 变为 5\n312: - **WHEN** `onCodeInterpreterUpdated` 被触发\n313: - **THEN** 记录 Warm Pool 激活日志，包含 pool size 值\n314: \n315: #### Scenario: Tombstone 处理\n316: \n317: - **GIVEN** informer 在缓存未同步时收到删除事件，obj 为 `cache.DeletedFinalStateUnknown`\n318: - **WHEN** `DeleteFunc` 被触发\n319: - **THEN** 从 `DeletedFinalStateUnknown.Obj` 提取对象并生成 session-id\n320: \n321: #### Scenario: 无 session-id label 的 CR 被忽略\n322: \n323: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR 无 `runtime.agentcube.io/session-id` label\n324: - **WHEN** `onAgentRuntimeAdded` 被触发\n325: - **THEN** 记录警告日志，不执行 Store 或 Router 操作\n326: \n327: ---\n328: \n329: ### Requirement: 会话生命周期 GC\n330: \n331: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_lifecycle.go` 中实现 `LifecycleManager`：\n332: \n333: ```go\n334: type LifecycleManager struct {\n335:     store         store.Store\n336:     checkInterval time.Duration\n337:     idleTimeout   time.Duration\n338:     maxDuration   time.Duration\n339:     clientset     clientset.Interface\n340: }\n341: ```\n342: \n343: `Start(ctx)` SHALL 启动后台 GC 协程，按 `checkInterval` 周期执行以下清理：\n344: \n345: 1. **TTL 过期清理（cleanupExpired）**：调用 `store.ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), batchSize)`，对每个过期会话调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID`\n346: 2. **空闲超时清理（cleanupIdle）**：调用 `store.ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-idleTimeout), batchSize)`，对每个不活跃会话调用 `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID`\n347: 3. **孤儿 CR 清理（cleanupOrphans）**：遍历 `store.ListSandboxes` 中的会话，通过 Lister 验证对应 CR 是否存在，若 CR 不存在则清理 Store 条目\n348: 4. **幽灵条目清理（cleanupGhosts）**：通过 Lister 列出所有 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CR，验证 Store 中是否有对应条目，若 Store 中缺失则补建\n349: \n350: `Stop()` SHALL 发送停止信号并等待 GC 协程退出（超时 10 秒）。\n351: \n352: **默认配置：**\n353: - `checkInterval`: 5 分钟\n354: - `idleTimeout`: 30 分钟（可被 CR 的 `spec.sessionTimeout` 覆盖）\n355: - `maxDuration`: 24 小时（可被 CR 的 `spec.maxSessionDuration` 覆盖）\n356: - `batchSize`: 100\n357: \n358: #### Scenario: TTL 过期会话被清理\n359: \n360: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 的 ExpiresAt 已过\n361: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupExpired`\n362: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-001\")` 被调用\n363: \n364: #### Scenario: 空闲超时会话被清理\n365: \n366: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-002` 的 LastActivityAt 为 35 分钟前，idleTimeout 为 30 分钟\n367: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupIdle`\n368: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-002\")` 被调用\n369: \n370: #### Scenario: 孤儿 CR 条目被清理\n371: \n372: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-003`，但对应 AgentRuntime CR 已被删除\n373: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupOrphans`\n374: - **THEN** `store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"sess-003\")` 被调用\n375: \n376: #### Scenario: 幽灵条目被补建\n377: \n378: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime CR `default/my-runtime` 存在且携带 session-id，但 Store 中无对应条目\n379: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行 `cleanupGhosts`\n380: - **THEN** `store.StoreSandbox` 被调用补建会话条目\n381: \n382: #### Scenario: GC 协程优雅停止\n383: \n384: - **GIVEN** GC 协程正在运行\n385: - **WHEN** `Stop()` 被调用\n386: - **THEN** GC 协程在 10 秒内退出\n387: \n388: #### Scenario: Store 不可用时 GC 不 panic\n389: \n390: - **GIVEN** Redis/Valkey 连接断开\n391: - **WHEN** GC 周期执行\n392: - **THEN** 记录错误日志，不 panic，下个周期重试\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ### Requirement: 代理流程会话感知增强\n397: \n398: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/proxy.go` 中增强代理逻辑：\n399: \n400: **成功路径（两次 LastActivityAt 更新）：**\n401: 1. 解析 session ID 后调用 `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, sessionID)`（第一次）\n402: 2. 执行 `forwardToSandbox` 反向代理\n403: 3. 代理成功后再次调用 `UpdateLastActivity(ctx, sessionID)`（第二次）\n404: \n405: **错误处理：**\n406: - `UpdateLastActivity` 失败 SHALL 仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程\n407: - 会话状态为 `terminated` 时，代理请求 SHALL 返回 410 Gone `{\"error\":\"session has been terminated\"}`\n408: \n409: **JWT 注入增强：**\n410: - 对于 Sandbox/SandboxClaim kind 的入口点，在代理前生成 JWT 并注入 `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n411: - JWT 签名失败 SHALL 返回 500 `{\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\",\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"}`\n412: \n413: **响应头注入：**\n414: - 所有代理响应 SHALL 携带 `x-agentcube-session-id` header，值为解析后的 session ID\n415: \n416: #### Scenario: 成功路径调用两次 UpdateLastActivity\n417: \n418: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `sess-001`，sandbox 解析成功且代理转发成功\n419: - **WHEN** invoke handler 完成\n420: - **THEN** `UpdateLastActivity` 被调用两次（解析后和转发后）\n421: \n422: #### Scenario: LastActivity 更新失败不阻断代理\n423: \n424: - **GIVEN** `UpdateLastActivity` 返回错误（Store 不可用）\n425: - **WHEN** sandbox 解析成功\n426: - **THEN** 代理仍然执行，错误仅被记录为 warning\n427: \n428: #### Scenario: 已终止会话返回 410\n429: \n430: - **GIVEN** 会话 `sess-001` 的 Status 为 `terminated`\n431: - **WHEN** 代理请求到达\n432: - **THEN** 响应 410，body 为 JSON `{\"error\":\"session has been terminated\"}`\n433: \n434: #### Scenario: 代理响应携带 session ID header\n435: \n436: - **GIVEN** session ID 为 `sess-001`\n437: - **WHEN** 代理响应返回\n438: - **THEN** 响应 header 包含 `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-001`\n439: \n440: ---\n441: \n442: ### Requirement: SessionManager 与 Store 集成\n443: \n444: The system SHALL 在 `NewSessionManager` 中注入 Store 实例：\n445: \n446: ```go\n447: func NewSessionManager(storeClient store.Store) (SessionManager, error)\n448: ```\n449: \n450: `GetSandboxBySession` 的会话解析流程 SHALL：\n451: 1. 若 `sessionID` 非空：调用 `storeClient.GetSandbox(ctx, sessionID)` 获取 `SandboxInfo`\n452: 2. 若 Store 返回 `ErrNotFound`：返回 `NewSessionNotFoundError(sessionID)`\n453: 3. 若 `sessionID` 为空：POST 到 WorkloadManager 创建 sandbox（AR-009 已有逻辑）\n454: 4. 创建成功后调用 `CreateSession(ctx, newInfo)` 写入 Store\n455: \n456: #### Scenario: 创建沙箱后写入 Store\n457: \n458: - **GIVEN** 空 sessionID，WorkloadManager 创建成功返回 `CreateSandboxResponse{SessionID: \"sess-new\", ...}`\n459: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n460: - **THEN** 构建 `SandboxInfo`\n461: - **AND** `CreateSession(ctx, newInfo)` 被调用写入 Store\n462: \n463: #### Scenario: 已知 sessionID 从 Store 获取\n464: \n465: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 `sess-001` 条目\n466: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySession(ctx, \"sess-001\", \"default\", \"my-runtime\", \"AgentRuntime\")` 被调用\n467: - **THEN** 返回对应的 `*types.SandboxInfo`\n468: \n469: ---\n470: \n471: ### Requirement: Server 集成会话管理组件\n472: \n473: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/server.go` 中扩展 `Server` 结构体，新增以下字段：\n474: \n475: ```go\n476: type Server struct {\n477:     // 现有字段（AR-009）\n478:     config         *Config\n479:     engine         *gin.Engine\n480:     httpServer     *http.Server\n481:     sessionManager SessionManager\n482:     storeClient    store.Store\n483:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n484:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n485: \n486:     // 新增字段（AR-010）\n487:     informerManager *InformerManager\n488:     lifecycleManager *LifecycleManager\n489: }\n490: ```\n491: \n492: `NewServer` SHALL 在构造函数中：\n493: 1. 初始化 `store.Store` 实例（通过 `store.Storage()`）\n494: 2. 构造 `InformerManager` 并传入 `router` 引用\n495: 3. 构造 `LifecycleManager` 并传入 `store` 和 `clientset`\n496: 4. 注册路由（含 informer 和 lifecycle 组件）\n497: \n498: `Start()` SHALL 在 HTTP 服务器启动前：\n499: 1. 启动 `InformerManager`（`im.Start(stopCh)`）\n500: 2. 启动 `LifecycleManager`（`lm.Start(ctx)`）\n501: \n502: `Shutdown(ctx)` SHALL 按以下顺序执行：\n503: 1. 停止 `LifecycleManager`\n504: 2. 停止 `InformerManager`\n505: 3. 优雅关闭 HTTP 服务器\n506: \n507: #### Scenario: Server 启动时 Informer 和 GC 同时运行\n508: \n509: - **GIVEN** `NewServer` 构造完成\n510: - **WHEN** `Start()` 被调用\n511: - **THEN** `InformerManager.Start` 和 `LifecycleManager.Start` 在 HTTP 服务器监听前被调用\n512: \n513: #### Scenario: Server 关闭时按序停止组件\n514: \n515: - **GIVEN** Server 正在运行\n516: - **WHEN** `Shutdown(ctx)` 被调用\n517: - **THEN** `LifecycleManager.Stop` 先执行，然后 `InformerManager` 停止，最后 HTTP 服务器关闭\n518: \n519: ---\n520: \n521: ### Requirement: Config 扩展会话相关配置\n522: \n523: The system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/config.go` 中扩展 `Config` 结构体，新增以下字段：\n524: \n525: | 字段 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n526: |------|------|--------|------|\n527: | `SessionCheckInterval time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `5 * time.Minute` | GC 检查间隔 |\n528: | `SessionIdleTimeout time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `30 * time.Minute` | 空闲超时 |\n529: | `SessionMaxDuration time.Duration` | `time.Duration` | `24 * time.Hour` | 最大会话时长 |\n530: | `StoreType string` | `string` | `\"\"`（使用环境变量） | 存储类型（redis/valkey） |\n531: \n532: CLI 标志 SHALL 支持：\n533: \n534: | Flag | 类型 | 默认值 |\n535: |------|------|--------|\n536: | `-session-check-interval` | duration | `5m` |\n537: | `-session-idle-timeout` | duration | `30m` |\n538: | `-session-max-duration` | duration | `24h` |\n539: | `-store-type` | string | `\"\"` |\n540: \n541: #### Scenario: 默认会话配置\n542: \n543: - **GIVEN** 未传入会话相关 CLI 标志\n544: - **WHEN** `NewDefaultConfig()` 被调用\n545: - **THEN** `SessionCheckInterval = 5m`，`SessionIdleTimeout = 30m`，`SessionMaxDuration = 24h`\n546: \n547: #### Scenario: 自定义会话超时\n548: \n549: - **GIVEN** CLI 标志 `-session-idle-timeout=1h -session-max-duration=48h`\n550: - **WHEN** `main()` 解析标志\n551: - **THEN** `Config.SessionIdleTimeout = 1h`，`Config.SessionMaxDuration = 48h`\n552: \n553: ---\n554: \n555: ### Requirement: 编译与测试门禁\n556: \n557: The system SHALL 满足以下门禁：\n558: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n559: 2. `go build ./pkg/store/...` 编译通过\n560: 3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n561: 4. `go test ./pkg/store/... -v` 全部通过\n562: 5. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n563: 6. `go test -race ./pkg/store/...` 无 data race 告警\n564: 7. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（使用 `slog` 或 `klog`）\n565: \n566: #### Scenario: pkg/router 编译通过\n567: \n568: - **GIVEN** 所有 router 代码已编写完成\n569: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/router/...` 执行\n570: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n571: \n572: #### Scenario: pkg/store 编译通过\n573: \n574: - **GIVEN** 所有 store 代码已编写完成\n575: - **WHEN** `go build ./pkg/store/...` 执行\n576: - **THEN** 无编译错误\n577: \n578: #### Scenario: 所有单元测试通过\n579: \n580: - **GIVEN** 测试用例已编写（含 SessionManager、Store、Informer、LifecycleManager）\n581: - **WHEN** `go test ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/... -v` 执行\n582: - **THEN** 所有测试通过\n583: \n584: #### Scenario: Race detector 无告警\n585: \n586: - **GIVEN** 并发场景测试已覆盖（Store 原子操作、Informer 回调、GC 协程）\n587: - **WHEN** `go test -race ./pkg/router/... ./pkg/store/...` 执行\n588: - **THEN** 无 data race 告警\n589: \n590: #### Scenario: 无 log.Printf 残留\n591: \n592: - **GIVEN** 所有日志已使用 `slog` 或 `klog`\n593: - **WHEN** `grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/ pkg/store/` 执行\n594: - **THEN** 无匹配结果\n\n(End of file - total 594 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010: Router 会话管理 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，在 AR-009（HTTP 反向代理核心）的基础上，扩展 SessionManager 接口、实现 Redis/Valkey Store 后端、激活 Informer 事件处理器、引入会话生命周期 GC，并增强代理流程的会话感知能力。本变更是对 AR-007（Reconciler 控制器）的下游消费方，同时依赖 session-store spec 中定义的存储契约。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: SessionManager 接口扩展\n\nThe system SHALL 在 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` 中扩展 `SessionManager` 接口，新增以下方法：\n\n```go\ntype SessionManager interface {\n    // 现有方法（AR-009）\n    GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n\n    // 新增方法（AR-010）\n    CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-010/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775828862491,"end":1775828862499}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775828863596,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a606a6001H0Ou1tSUW3CHIi","messageID":"msg_d77a5f300001Om7ZmvJB7jSwFj","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7b38bff7c8e2409a91e052e3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-010: Router 会话管理\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 agentcube 项目的 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，包括会话创建、解析、存储、生命周期管理和会话感知的流量路由。该模块将与 Redis/Valkey 存储后端集成，利用 client-go 的 Informer 机制监听 CRD 变更，实现动态会话路由和自动过期清理。\n6: \n7: ## Scope\n8: \n9: ### In Scope\n10: \n11: 1. **会话解析与路由**\n12:    - 从 `x-agentcube-session-id` 请求头提取会话标识\n13:    - 基于会话 ID 查询 SandboxInfo 并解析目标 Pod 入口点\n14:    - 支持 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两种会话类型\n15:    - 会话未命中时的降级策略（转发至 WorkloadManager 创建新沙箱）\n16: \n17: 2. **会话存储集成**\n18:    - 实现 Redis/Valkey 后端的 Store 接口（当前为 stub）\n19:    - 支持 SandboxInfo 的序列化存储与快速检索\n20:    - 会话元数据缓存（SessionID、SandboxName、PodIP、EntryPoints、ExpiresAt、Status）\n21:    - 原子性更新会话最后活跃时间（`LastActivityAt`）\n22: \n23: 3. **会话生命周期管理**\n24:    - TTL 过期自动清理（基于 CRD 定义的 `MaxSessionDuration`）\n25:    - 空闲超时检测与清理（基于 `SessionTimeout` 配置）\n26:    - 幽灵会话清理（存储中存在但 CR 已删除的条目）\n27:    - 孤儿 CR 扫描（CR 存在但存储中无对应条目）\n28: \n29: 4. **Informer 驱动的会话同步**\n30:    - 使用 `SharedInformerFactory` 监听 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n31:    - 通过 `AgentRuntimeInformer` 和 `CodeInterpreterInformer` 获取会话配置\n32:    - 事件处理器更新本地会话缓存和路由表\n33:    - 利用 `Lister` 接口进行本地缓存查询，减少 API Server 压力\n34: \n35: 5. **会话感知代理增强**\n36:    - 代理请求前后更新会话活跃时间\n37:    - JWT 令牌注入（针对 Sandbox/SandboxClaim 类型的入口点）\n38:    - 响应头注入 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n39:    - 会话状态异常时的错误映射（SessionNotFoundError、SandboxTemplateNotFoundError）\n40: \n41: ### Out of Scope\n42: \n43: - WorkloadManager 侧的沙箱创建逻辑（由其他 AR 处理）\n44: - 沙箱 Pod 的生命周期管理（创建、删除、扩缩容）\n45: - 高级会话特性（会话持久化、跨会话状态共享）\n46: - WebSocket/gRPC 会话支持（后续迭代）\n47: \n48: ## Impact Analysis\n49: \n50: ### Dependencies\n51: \n52: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n53: |------|------|------|\n54: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | Informer/Lister 访问 CRD 会话配置 | 需确保 client-go 版本与 API Server 兼容（v0.34.1） |\n55: | `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` 或 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` | 会话存储后端 | 新增运行时依赖，需配置连接池和超时 |\n56: | `pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go` | SandboxInfo 模型定义 | 共享类型，需保持字段同步 |\n57: | `pkg/store/store.go` | Store 接口定义 | 需实现 Redis/Valkey 后端替换当前 stub |\n58: \n59: ### Affected Components\n60: \n61: - **pkg/router/session_manager.go**: 扩展 SessionManager 接口，增加会话创建、更新、删除方法\n62: - **pkg/router/proxy.go**: 增强代理逻辑，集成会话活跃时间更新和错误处理\n63: - **pkg/router/informer.go**: 激活 Informer 事件处理器，从 stub 改为实际更新会话缓存\n64: - **pkg/store/**: 实现 Redis/Valkey 后端（当前 Storage() 返回 nil）\n65: - **pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_lifecycle.go**: 会话生命周期管理可能从 WorkloadManager 迁移至 Router\n66: \n67: ### Risk Assessment\n68: \n69: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n70: |------|------|----------|\n71: | Redis/Valkey 不可用导致会话丢失 | 高 | 实现本地内存缓存降级，定期同步到存储 |\n72: | Informer 同步延迟导致路由到过期会话 | 中 | 设置合理的 `defaultResync`，实现存储查询 fallback |\n73: | 高并发下会话状态竞争 | 中 | 使用 Redis 原子操作（SET NX/XX），乐观锁更新 |\n74: | 会话清理不及时导致资源泄漏 | 中 | 定时 GC 协程 + TTL 自动过期双保险 |\n75: \n76: ## Alternatives Considered\n77: \n78: ### 1. 会话状态完全存储在 Kubernetes CR 中\n79: \n80: **优点**: 单一事实来源、无需额外存储组件、天然支持持久化  \n81: **缺点**: API Server 读写延迟高、频繁更新 LastActivityAt 会增加 API Server 压力、不适合高频会话场景  \n82: **决策**: 不采用。会话活跃时间更新频率高（每次请求），使用 Redis/Valkey 更适合低延迟读写。\n83: \n84: ### 2. 会话状态仅存储在本地内存中\n85: \n86: **优点**: 极致性能、无外部依赖、实现简单  \n87: **缺点**: Router 实例重启后会话丢失、多实例部署时会话不一致、无法水平扩展  \n88: **决策**: 不采用。agentcube 需要支持多副本部署，会话状态必须集中存储。\n89: \n90: ### 3. Redis/Valkey 集中存储 + 本地缓存降级（选定方案）\n91: \n92: **优点**: \n93: - 支持多实例水平扩展\n94: - Redis/Valkey 提供原生 TTL 过期机制\n95: - 本地缓存可在存储不可用时提供降级服务\n96: - 与现有 pkg/store 接口设计对齐\n97: \n98: **缺点**: \n99: - 增加运维复杂度（需部署 Redis/Valkey 集群）\n100: - 需要处理缓存一致性问题\n101: - 网络分区时可能出现会话状态分歧\n102: \n103: **决策**: 采用。符合 agentcube 的分布式架构需求，M 规模的实现工作量可控。\n104: \n105: ## Implementation Notes\n106: \n107: ### 核心接口扩展\n108: \n109: ```go\n110: type SessionManager interface {\n111:     // 现有方法\n112:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n113:     \n114:     // 新增方法\n115:     CreateSession(ctx context.Context, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n116:     UpdateSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n117:     DeleteSession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n118:     UpdateLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n119:     ListSessions(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n120: }\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ### Store 接口实现\n124: \n125: ```go\n126: // Redis/Valkey 后端实现 pkg/store/store.go 中定义的接口\n127: type RedisStore struct {\n128:     client redis.UniversalClient\n129:     codec  Codec // SandboxInfo 序列化/反序列化\n130: }\n131: \n132: func (s *RedisStore) StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n133: func (s *RedisStore) GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n134: func (s *RedisStore) UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n135: func (s *RedisStore) DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n136: func (s *RedisStore) ListSandboxes(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n137: func (s *RedisStore) UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, lastActivityTime interface{}) error\n138: ```\n139: \n140: ### Informer 事件处理\n141: \n142: ```go\n143: // 从 stub 改为实际处理\n144: agentRuntimeInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n145:     AddFunc:    m.onAgentRuntimeAdded,    // 注册新会话路由\n146:     UpdateFunc: m.onAgentRuntimeUpdated,  // 更新会话配置\n147:     DeleteFunc: m.onAgentRuntimeDeleted,  // 清理过期会话\n148: })\n149: \n150: codeInterpreterInformer.Informer().AddEventHandler(cache.ResourceEventHandlerFuncs{\n151:     AddFunc:    m.onCodeInterpreterAdded,\n152:     UpdateFunc: m.onCodeInterpreterUpdated,\n153:     DeleteFunc: m.onCodeInterpreterDeleted,\n154: })\n155: ```\n156: \n157: ### 会话生命周期 GC\n158: \n159: ```go\n160: type LifecycleManager struct {\n161:     store          store.Store\n162:     checkInterval  time.Duration\n163:     idleTimeout    time.Duration\n164:     maxDuration    time.Duration\n165: }\n166: \n167: func (lm *LifecycleManager) Start(ctx context.Context) {\n168:     go lm.runGC(ctx)\n169: }\n170: \n171: func (lm *LifecycleManager) runGC(ctx context.Context) {\n172:     ticker := time.NewTicker(lm.checkInterval)\n173:     defer ticker.Stop()\n174:     \n175:     for {\n176:         select {\n177:         case <-ctx.Done():\n178:             return\n179:         case <-ticker.C:\n180:             lm.cleanupExpired()    // TTL 过期清理\n181:             lm.cleanupIdle()       // 空闲超时清理\n182:             lm.cleanupOrphans()    // 孤儿 CR 清理\n183:             lm.cleanupGhosts()     // 幽灵条目清理\n184:         }\n185:     }\n186: }\n187: ```\n188: \n189: ### 目录结构\n190: \n191: ```\n192: pkg/router/\n193: ├── session_manager.go     # SessionManager 接口和实现（扩展）\n194: ├── session_store.go       # Redis/Valkey Store 实现（新增）\n195: ├── session_lifecycle.go   # 会话生命周期 GC（新增）\n196: ├── proxy.go               # 代理逻辑（增强会话感知）\n197: ├── informer.go            # Informer 事件处理（从 stub 改为实际）\n198: ├── server.go              # Server 集成会话管理组件\n199: ├── config.go              # 配置（新增会话相关配置项）\n200: └── errors.go              # 会话相关错误定义\n201: ```\n202: \n203: ## Acceptance Criteria\n204: \n205: 1. **会话创建与解析**\n206:    - [ ] 支持通过 `x-agentcube-session-id` 头解析现有会话\n207:    - [ ] 会话不存在时能正确返回 SessionNotFoundError\n208:    - [ ] 空会话 ID 时能正确转发至 WorkloadManager 创建新沙箱\n209: \n210: 2. **存储后端**\n211:    - [ ] Redis/Valkey Store 实现通过所有 store 接口测试\n212:    - [ ] 支持会话 TTL 自动过期\n213:    - [ ] 支持 LastActivityAt 原子更新\n214: \n215: 3. **Informer 集成**\n216:    - [ ] AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter 变更事件能正确更新会话缓存\n217:    - [ ] Informer 启动后能完成初始同步\n218:    - [ ] 存储不可用时能 fallback 到 Lister 本地缓存\n219: \n220: 4. **生命周期管理**\n221:    - [ ] TTL 过期会话能被定时 GC 清理\n222:    - [ ] 空闲超时会话能被检测并清理\n223:    - [ ] 孤儿 CR 和幽灵条目能被识别并清理\n224: \n225: 5. **代理增强**\n226:    - [ ] 代理请求前后正确更新 LastActivityAt\n227:    - [ ] JWT 令牌正确注入到 Sandbox/SandboxClaim 入口点\n228:    - [ ] 响应头包含 `x-agentcube-session-id`\n229: \n230: ## Status\n231: \n232: - [ ] 提案审查\n233: - [ ] 实现\n234: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 234 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-010: Router 会话管理\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 agentcube 项目的 `pkg/router` 模块实现完整的会话管理能力，包括会话创建、解析、存储、生命周期管理和会话感知的流量路由。该模块将与 Redis/Valkey 存储后端集成，利用 client-go 的 Informer 机制监听 CRD 变更，实现动态会话路由和自动过期清理。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **会话解析与路由**\n   - 从 `x-agentcube-session-id` 请求头提取会话标识\n   - 基于会话 ID 查询 SandboxInfo 并解析目标 Pod 入口点\n   - 支持 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 两种会话类型\n   - 会话未命中时的降级策略（转发至 WorkloadManager 创建新沙箱）\n\n2. **会话存储集成**\n   - 实现 Redis/Valkey 后端的 Store 接口（当前为 stub）\n   - 支持 SandboxInfo 的序列化存储与快速检索\n   - 会话元数据缓存（SessionID、SandboxName、PodIP、EntryPoints、ExpiresAt、Status）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775828863589,"end":1775828863595}}}}
