{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775828866890,"sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","part":{"id":"prt_d77a6138e001HGqZwhtJF8QHSL","messageID":"msg_d77a5f300001Om7ZmvJB7jSwFj","sessionID":"ses_2885cc624ffe0LB44CoY3k3GVD","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_34cec96d65ca4d698e8f8601","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: `pkg/router` 是 AgentCube 系统的流量入口，负责将外部 HTTP 请求反向代理到 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 sandbox pod。核心职责：\n8: \n9: 1. **Session 解析与 Sandbox 创建**：通过 session ID 从 store 查找 sandbox，或在 session ID 为空时通过 WorkloadManager 创建新 sandbox\n10: 2. **HTTP 反向代理**：将请求代理到 sandbox 的 entry point，注入 RS256 JWT 签名\n11: 3. **动态服务发现**：通过 client-go Informer 监听 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n12: 4. **流量治理**：负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制\n13: \n14: ### 1.2 包结构\n15: \n16: ```\n17: pkg/router/\n18: ├── config.go              # Config 结构体与默认值\n19: ├── server.go              # Server 结构体、构造函数、启动/关闭\n20: ├── session_manager.go     # SessionManager 接口与实现\n21: ├── jwt.go                 # JWTManager、密钥管理、token 生成\n22: ├── proxy.go               # ReverseProxy 封装、Director、ErrorHandler\n23: ├── backend.go             # Backend 管理、健康检查\n24: ├── loadbalancer.go        # Round-Robin、Least-Connections 负载均衡\n25: ├── middleware.go          # 并发限制、日志、Trace ID 中间件\n26: ├── informer.go            # CRD Informer 集成、事件处理\n27: ├── router.go              # Router 接口、路由表管理\n28: ├── errors.go              # 自定义错误类型\n29: └── *_test.go              # 单元测试\n30: \n31: cmd/router/\n32: └── main.go                # CLI 入口、标志解析\n33: ```\n34: \n35: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n36: \n37: ```\n38: pkg/router\n39: ├── github.com/gin-gonic/gin              # HTTP 路由引擎\n40: ├── github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5          # RS256 JWT 签名\n41: ├── golang.org/x/net/http2                # HTTP/2 支持\n42: ├── k8s.io/api                            # K8s API 类型\n43: ├── k8s.io/apimachinery                   # errors, schema, runtime\n44: ├── k8s.io/client-go                      # rest, kubernetes.Interface\n45: ├── k8s.io/klog/v2                        # 结构化日志\n46: ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go        # 生成的 typed client\n47: ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1  # CRD 类型\n48: ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types           # 共享类型（Kind, SandboxInfo）\n49: ├── github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store                  # Session store 接口\n50: └── net/http/httputil                     # Go 标准库反向代理\n51: ```\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## 2. 数据结构\n56: \n57: ### 2.1 Config\n58: \n59: ```go\n60: type Config struct {\n61:     Port                  string // 监听端口，默认 \"8080\"\n62:     Debug                 bool   // Gin debug 模式\n63:     EnableTLS             bool   // 是否启用 TLS\n64:     TLSCert               string // TLS 证书路径\n65:     TLSKey                string // TLS 私钥路径\n66:     MaxConcurrentRequests int    // 最大并发请求数，默认 1000\n67: }\n68: ```\n69: \n70: ### 2.2 Server\n71: \n72: ```go\n73: type Server struct {\n74:     config         *Config\n75:     engine         *gin.Engine\n76:     httpServer     *http.Server\n77:     sessionManager SessionManager\n78:     storeClient    store.Store\n79:     httpTransport  *http.Transport\n80:     jwtManager     *JWTManager\n81: }\n82: ```\n83: \n84: - `httpTransport`: `IdleConnTimeout: 0`（不回收空闲连接），`DisableCompression: false`\n85: - `httpServer`: `ReadTimeout: 30s`, `IdleTimeout: 90s`, 支持 h2c 明文升级\n86: \n87: ### 2.3 SessionManager\n88: \n89: ```go\n90: type SessionManager interface {\n91:     GetSandboxBySession(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, namespace string, name string, kind string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n92: }\n93: \n94: type manager struct {\n95:     storeClient     store.Store\n96:     workloadMgrAddr string\n97:     httpClient      *http.Client\n98: }\n99: ```\n100: \n101: - `httpClient.Timeout`: 2 分钟\n102: - Transport: `MaxIdleConnsPerHost: 100`, `DisableCompression: false`, HTTP/2 `ReadIdleTimeout: 30s`, `PingTimeout: 15s`\n103: \n104: ### 2.4 JWTManager\n105: \n106: ```go\n107: const (\n108:     rsaKeySize         = 2048\n109:     jwtExpiration      = 5 * time.Minute\n110:     IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"\n111:     PrivateKeyDataKey  = \"private.pem\"\n112:     PublicKeyDataKey   = \"public.pem\"\n113: )\n114: \n115: var IdentityNamespace = \"default\" // init(): AGENTCUBE_NAMESPACE 覆盖\n116: \n117: type JWTManager struct {\n118:     privateKey *rsa.PrivateKey\n119:     publicKey  *rsa.PublicKey\n120:     clientset  kubernetes.Interface\n121: }\n122: ```\n123: \n124: - `NewJWTManager()`: 生成 RSA 2048-bit 密钥对\n125: - `GenerateToken(claims)`: RS256 签名，基础 claims `exp`, `iat`, `iss=\"agentcube-router\"`\n126: - `TryStoreOrLoadJWTKeySecret(ctx)`: 创建或加载 K8s Secret 中的密钥对\n127: \n128: ### 2.5 Router 与 Backend\n129: \n130: ```go\n131: type Router interface {\n132:     AddRoute(pattern string, backend Backend) error\n133:     RemoveRoute(pattern string) error\n134:     ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)\n135: }\n136: \n137: type Backend struct {\n138:     URL      *url.URL\n139:     Weight   int\n140:     Healthy  bool\n141: }\n142: \n143: type routerImpl struct {\n144:     mu       sync.RWMutex\n145:     routes   map[string]Backend\n146:     lb       LoadBalancer\n147: }\n148: ```\n149: \n150: ### 2.6 LoadBalancer\n151: \n152: ```go\n153: type LoadBalancer interface {\n154:     Select(backends []Backend) (*Backend, error)\n155: }\n156: \n157: type RoundRobinBalancer struct {\n158:     mu      sync.Mutex\n159:     current int\n160: }\n161: \n162: type LeastConnectionsBalancer struct {\n163:     connections map[string]*atomic.Int64\n164: }\n165: ```\n166: \n167: ### 2.7 BackendHealthChecker\n168: \n169: ```go\n170: type BackendHealthChecker struct {\n171:     interval          time.Duration // 默认 30s\n172:     consecutiveFail   int           // 标记不健康阈值，默认 3\n173:     consecutiveSuccess int          // 标记健康阈值，默认 2\n174:     checker           func(*url.URL) (bool, error)\n175: }\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ### 2.8 自定义错误类型\n179: \n180: ```go\n181: type SessionNotFoundError struct {\n182:     SessionID string\n183: }\n184: \n185: type SandboxTemplateNotFoundError struct {\n186:     Namespace string\n187:     Name      string\n188:     Kind      string\n189: }\n190: \n191: func (e *SessionNotFoundError) Error() string\n192: func (e *SandboxTemplateNotFoundError) Error() string\n193: ```\n194: \n195: ---\n196: \n197: ## 3. API 契约\n198: \n199: ### 3.1 路由注册\n200: \n201: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n202: |--------|------|------------|---------|\n203: | GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n204: | GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n205: | GET, POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path` | `gin.Logger`, `gin.Recovery`, `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | `handleAgentInvoke` |\n206: | GET, POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path` | 同上 | `handleCodeInterpreterInvoke` |\n207: \n208: ### 3.2 Health 端点响应\n209: \n210: **Liveness:**\n211: ```json\n212: GET /health/live → 200 {\"status\":\"alive\"}\n213: ```\n214: \n215: **Readiness:**\n216: ```json\n217: GET /health/ready → 200 {\"status\":\"ready\"}\n218: GET /health/ready → 503 {\"status\":\"not ready\",\"error\":\"session manager not available\"}\n219: ```\n220: \n221: ### 3.3 反向代理行为\n222: \n223: **Upstream URL 确定：**\n224: 1. 从 `SandboxInfo.EntryPoints` 查找第一个 `path` 前缀匹配 invocation path 的 entry point\n225: 2. 无匹配时使用第一个 entry point\n226: 3. EntryPoints 为空时返回 404 `{\"error\":\"no entry point found for sandbox\"}`\n227: \n228: **Director 设置：**\n229: - `req.URL.Path`: 规范化路径（Gin `*path` 无前导 `/` 时自动添加）\n230: - `req.URL.RawPath`: 清空\n231: - `req.Host`: `targetURL.Host`\n232: - `X-Forwarded-Host`: 原始请求 `Host`\n233: - `X-Forwarded-Proto`: `\"https\"`（TLS 存在）或 `\"http\"`\n234: - `X-Forwarded-For`: 追加客户端 IP\n235: - `Authorization`: `Bearer <JWT>`（仅 `Sandbox`/`SandboxClaim` kind）\n236: \n237: **ModifyResponse:**\n238: - 设置响应 header `x-agentcube-session-id` 为 resolved session ID\n239: \n240: ### 3.4 JWT 注入\n241: \n242: 对 `Sandbox` 和 `SandboxClaim` kind 的 sandbox：\n243: - 代理前生成 JWT token\n244: - 设置 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 到代理请求\n245: - JWT 签名失败时返回 500 `{\"code\":\"JWT_SIGNING_FAILED\",\"error\":\"failed to sign request\"}`\n246: \n247: ### 3.5 代理错误映射\n248: \n249: | 错误信息 | HTTP 状态码 | 响应体 |\n250: |----------|-------------|--------|\n251: | 包含 `\"connection refused\"` | 502 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}` |\n252: | 包含 `\"timeout\"` | 504 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox timeout\"}` |\n253: | 其他错误 | 502 | `{\"error\":\"sandbox unreachable\"}` |\n254: \n255: ### 3.6 并发限制中间件\n256: \n257: - 基于 buffered channel 的信号量，容量 `MaxConcurrentRequests`\n258: - 槽位耗尽时返回 429 `{\"error\":\"server overloaded, please try again later\",\"code\":\"SERVER_OVERLOADED\"}`\n259: - 仅应用于 `/v1` 路由组，health 端点不受限制\n260: \n261: ### 3.7 Last-activity 更新\n262: \n263: - sandbox 解析成功后调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, time.Now())`\n264: - `forwardToSandbox` 返回后再次调用\n265: - 失败仅记录 warning 日志，不阻断代理流程\n266: \n267: ---\n268: \n269: ## 4. 错误处理\n270: \n271: ### 4.1 错误分类\n272: \n273: | 错误类型 | 来源 | 处理方式 |\n274: |----------|------|----------|\n275: | `SessionNotFoundError` | Store 中不存在 session | 404 JSON |\n276: | `SandboxTemplateNotFoundError` | WorkloadManager 返回非 200 | 404 JSON |\n277: | JWT 签名失败 | `GenerateToken` 返回错误 | 500 JSON `JWT_SIGNING_FAILED` |\n278: | 连接拒绝 | 反向代理 ErrorHandler | 502 `sandbox unreachable` |\n279: | 超时 | 反向代理 ErrorHandler | 504 `sandbox timeout` |\n280: | 并发超限 | `concurrencyLimitMiddleware` | 429 `SERVER_OVERLOADED` |\n281: | K8s API 错误 | `apierrors.APIStatus` | 使用 status code，500 时替换消息为 `internal server error` |\n282: \n283: ### 4.2 错误辅助函数\n284: \n285: ```go\n286: func handleGetSandboxError(c *gin.Context, err error) {\n287:     if statusErr, ok := err.(apierrors.APIStatus); ok {\n288:         code := statusErr.Status().Code\n289:         if code == 0 {\n290:             code = http.StatusInternalServerError\n291:         }\n292:         message := statusErr.Status().Message\n293:         if message == \"\" {\n294:             message = err.Error()\n295:         }\n296:         if code == http.StatusInternalServerError {\n297:             message = \"internal server error\"\n298:         }\n299:         c.JSON(int(code), gin.H{\"error\": message})\n300:         return\n301:     }\n302:     c.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{\"error\": \"internal server error\"})\n303: }\n304: ```\n305: \n306: ### 4.3 日志策略\n307: \n308: - 使用 `slog` 或 `klog`，禁止 `log.Printf`\n309: - 结构化日志字段：`method`, `path`, `status`, `duration_ms`, `trace_id`\n310: - 警告级别：store 更新失败、service account token 读取失败（非 NotExist）、非 in-cluster JWT 密钥初始化\n311: \n312: ---\n313: \n314: ## 5. 测试策略\n315: \n316: ### 5.1 单元测试覆盖\n317: \n318: | 文件 | 测试内容 |\n319: |------|----------|\n320: | `config_test.go` | 默认值、CLI 标志解析、`MaxConcurrentRequests <= 0` 时 NewServer 设为 1000 |\n321: | `server_test.go` | Debug/Release 模式、JWT 初始化失败、`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` 未设置、TLS 配置验证 |\n322: | `session_manager_test.go` | session 查找、session 创建、Store NotFound、WorkloadManager 非 200、token 附加 |\n323: | `jwt_test.go` | token 生成、claims 验证、RS256 算法、Secret 创建/加载、ephemeral keys 路径 |\n324: | `proxy_test.go` | Director 设置、ModifyResponse、upstream URL 确定、协议拼接、path 规范化 |\n325: | `backend_test.go` | 健康检查成功/失败、连续失败阈值、单次失败不立即标记 |\n326: | `loadbalancer_test.go` | Round-Robin 循环、跳过不健康、Least-Connections 选择、全不健康错误 |\n327: | `middleware_test.go` | 并发限制通过/拒绝、槽位释放、health 端点不受限、Trace ID 注入 |\n328: | `router_test.go` | 路由添加/删除/重复/幂等、并发安全、ServeHTTP 匹配/404 |\n329: | `informer_test.go` | CRD 事件处理、路由表更新、Lister 缓存查询 |\n330: \n331: ### 5.2 并发测试\n332: \n333: ```bash\n334: go test -race ./pkg/router/...\n335: ```\n336: \n337: 覆盖场景：\n338: - 并发 `AddRoute`/`RemoveRoute`\n339: - 并发负载均衡选择\n340: - 并发健康检查状态更新\n341: - 并发中间件槽位获取/释放\n342: \n343: ### 5.3 门禁要求\n344: \n345: 1. `go build ./pkg/router/...` 编译通过\n346: 2. `go build ./cmd/router/...` 编译通过\n347: 3. `go test ./pkg/router/... -v` 全部通过\n348: 4. `go test -race ./pkg/router/...` 无 data race 告警\n349: 5. 无 `log.Printf` 残留（`grep -rn 'log\\.Printf' pkg/router/` 无匹配）\n350: \n351: ### 5.4 Mock 策略\n352: \n353: - `store.Store`: 使用接口 mock 实现 NotFound/成功场景\n354: - `kubernetes.Interface`: 使用 `client-go` fake clientset\n355: - WorkloadManager HTTP: 使用 `httptest.NewServer`\n356: - Informer: 使用 fake clientset + 手动触发事件\n357: \n358: ---\n359: \n360: ## 6. 实现步骤\n361: \n362: ### Phase 1: 基础结构（Day 1-2）\n363: \n364: 1. 创建 `pkg/router/config.go` — Config 结构体与默认值\n365: 2. 创建 `pkg/router/errors.go` — 自定义错误类型\n366: 3. 创建 `pkg/router/jwt.go` — JWTManager、密钥管理\n367: 4. 创建 `pkg/router/session_manager.go` — SessionManager 接口与实现\n368: 5. 编写对应单元测试\n369: \n370: ### Phase 2: 反向代理核心（Day 3-4）\n371: \n372: 1. 创建 `pkg/router/proxy.go` — ReverseProxy 封装、Director、ErrorHandler\n373: 2. 创建 `pkg/router/backend.go` — Backend 管理、健康检查\n374: 3. 创建 `pkg/router/loadbalancer.go` — Round-Robin、Least-Connections\n375: 4. 创建 `pkg/router/middleware.go` — 并发限制、日志、Trace ID\n376: 5. 编写对应单元测试\n377: \n378: ### Phase 3: 路由与服务器（Day 5-6）\n379: \n380: 1. 创建 `pkg/router/router.go` — Router 接口、路由表管理\n381: 2. 创建 `pkg/router/informer.go` — CRD Informer 集成、事件处理\n382: 3. 创建 `pkg/router/server.go` — Server 结构体、构造函数、路由注册、Start/Stop\n383: 4. 创建 `cmd/router/main.go` — CLI 入口、标志解析\n384: 5. 编写集成测试\n385: \n386: ### Phase 4: 集成与门禁（Day 7）\n387: \n388: 1. 运行 `go build ./pkg/router/... ./cmd/router/...`\n389: 2. 运行 `go test ./pkg/router/... -v`\n390: 3. 运行 `go test -race ./pkg/router/...`\n391: 4. 检查 `log.Printf` 残留\n392: 5. 修复所有问题，确保门禁通过\n393: \n394: ---\n395: \n396: ## 7. 后续变更\n397: \n398: | 变更 | 描述 | 优先级 |\n399: |------|------|--------|\n400: | AR-010 | 高级流量治理（灰度发布、A/B 测试） | P1 |\n401: | AR-011 | WebSocket/gRPC 代理支持 | P2 |\n402: | AR-012 | 基于 Prometheus 的动态负载均衡 | P2 |\n403: | AR-013 | 分布式追踪集成（OpenTelemetry） | P3 |\n404: | AR-014 | TLS 证书自动轮转 | P3 |\n405: \n406: ### 已知限制\n407: \n408: - 当前不支持 per-backend 超时配置（使用全局 `http.Transport`）\n409: - 健康检查路径固定为 `/health`，后续可配置化\n410: - 负载均衡策略仅支持 Round-Robin 和 Least-Connections，后续可扩展 Weighted Round-Robin\n411: - JWT 密钥固定 RS256，后续可支持 ES256 等其他算法\n\n(End of file - total 411 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`pkg/router` 是 AgentCube 系统的流量入口，负责将外部 HTTP 请求反向代理到 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的 sandbox pod。核心职责：\n\n1. **Session 解析与 Sandbox 创建**：通过 session ID 从 store 查找 sandbox，或在 session ID 为空时通过 WorkloadManager 创建新 sandbox\n2. **HTTP 反向代理**：将请求代理到 sandbox 的 entry point，注入 RS256 JWT 签名\n3. **动态服务发现**：通过 client-go Informer 监听 AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter CRD 变更\n4. **流量治理**：负载均衡、健康检查、并发限制\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/router/\n├── config.go              # Config 结构体与默认值\n├── server.go              # Server 结构体、构造函数、启动/关闭\n├── session_manager.go     # SessionManager 接口与实现","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md","time":{"start":1775828866883,"end":1775828866888}}}}
